                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman</hi>, 345). The prisoner was given into my custody at the Cheshire Cheese, with this crown—ho gave his name, Arthur Pope—he was taken before the Magistrate at Guildhall, remanded till the 25th, and then discharged.</p>
